  "remarks": "Sharia amir of Al-Nusrah Front for the People of the Levant (QDe.137) as\nof early 2014. Reportedly died in the Syrian Arab Republic on 2 April 2024, Mother’s name: Subhah Muhammad Sayf. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 4 Dec. 2019 Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded on 30 October 2023.  INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
